Class Intersection

  • java.lang.Object
    • component.Tile
      • component.Intersection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StopSign, TrafficLight

    public abstract class Intersection
extends Tile
    Intersection is the Abstract Class that both StopSign and TrafficLight extend from. Has members including: type, increment, and built-in allowed travel directions.

    3.0
    Author:
    Reid Stagemeyer
